      • Command

        public Command(WordData main,
               List<String> answers,
               String word,
               String preword,
               boolean smart)
        Creates an instance of a command class to find corrections.
        Parameters:
        main - A worddata instance which contains references to the trie and bigram/frequency
        answers - List of the best corrections
        word - word we are generating solutions based off of
        preword - the word, if any, that came before word
        smart - boolean that determines whether to use smart or default ranking

      • lHelper

        public void lHelper(Node node,
                    List<Integer> prevRow,
                    int prevLength,
                    int max)
        Helper to lev distance that caluclates the lev distance between a current node and word. It also estimates if there are viable children to consider
        Parameters:
        node - the current node we are considering for lev
        prevRow - the lev row calculations of the previous node, which helps us calculate the current lev faster
        prevLength - length of the value of the last node
        max - max lev distance for viability

      • continueL

        public Boolean continueL(List<Integer> row,
                         int max)
        A boolean checker to determine if we should calulate lev on children. Only continues if it's possible for future nodes to have a lev less than or equal to max, which is only possible if such a value already exists somewhere on the current node
        Parameters:
        row - the current row of lev value calculations
        max - max lev distance for viablity
        Returns:
        true if and only if there is a number in row less than or equal to max
